The paper deals with the controllability of networked systems, which is a topic in control theory. Therefore, cs.SY (Systems and Control) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also involves the analysis of network topology, which falls under the scope of cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems) and cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper may also involve machine learning techniques, which could place it under cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
